title: Knife Master
description: Throw the knife at the target board. Score double points for hitting the bullsye. Sounds easy? As you progress further, you'll need every single ounce of skill and finesse in knife throwing. Not to mention, you'll need impeccable timing too. One miss of the knife, and you're out! Similar to darts, fans of knife throwing and all throwing sports will love this game.
instructions: Throw knives at targets. Extremely challenging!

title: Billiard Neon
description: Billiard Neon is a fun game of billiards. Try to hit all the balls in the hole, but be careful with the 8-ball, it can cause the game to end. You can play against another player (PVP) or against the computer (PVC). Play and have fun.
instructions: Mouse or tap to play.

title: Climb the Ladder
description: Do you want to climb the ladder? The ladder here is unusual! He has infinite height! The possibilities are endless. You need quick reflexes to have more combos. They can also consistently get higher grades. Mind the ladder is not very secure! Catch the beat and change hands!
instructions: Tap to play.

title: Square Jet
description: Square Jet is a minimalist platformer game that is pretty addicting and fun to play. Help the little guy to move on the platform and pass through each level fill with various dangerous obstacles by using his jetpack to fly up. The level increases in difficulty as the level progress and makes it challenging.
instructions: Use left/right arrow to move, press up arrow to jump and press again and hold to fly.

title: Arrow Twist
description: Push the Arrow by tapping when itâ€™s facing the right direction. Super intuitive one-touch controls will have you hooked for hours! How far can you go?
instructions: Touch/Click to push the arrow.

title: Pixel Archer Save The Princess
description: Become the archer hero by saving the beautiful and sweet princess who is in trouble. You will face several enemies and warriors along the way, try to hit as levers precisely to free it. There are some balloons scattered throughout the scenarios, each balloon has an important function for the game, but be careful, as some of them can be dangerous! Have a good time.
instructions: Touch the screen to shoot

title: Anime Love Balls Girls
description: Different girls are waiting for your actions.Try to earn their love.Connect girls ball to earn their loveRemember your time is limited. How much love can you earn?
instructions: Connect 3 or more same girl ball.The more balls the more points you earn.Remember your time is limited.

title: Super Heels
description: Super Heels is undoubtedly the most interesting new arcade games this year. It has addictive level design and 3D art style, as well as very funny high heel parkour and heel collecting gameplay!
instructions: Drag to move.

title: Bomb Prank
description: The time countdown begins and the bomb you are trying to hand over has not yet been delivered? Exciting and fun multiplayer arena game, The bomb that was ignited, who all want to stay away from it, but the bomb can only be passed between each player, can you deliver his hot Dangerous thing to others out in the last seconds?
instructions: Drap and slide to move.

title: Can You Reach 8K
description: Welcome to our site where we present our new game Can You Reach 8K? In this game you have to combine three or more identical numbers and double their value. Your goal is reach 8k!
instructions: Use mouse or touch the screen!

title: Pencil Rush
description: This world needs a little color! Pick up your tool â€“ a colorful pencil & start the challenge! Swipe pencils, trace and race your way along the obstacle course. (You gotta avoid those obstacles. Hit them, and itâ€™s game over!) Add to your color collection by picking up more pencils along the run. Run and make it to the finish line where you can color an amazing picture.
instructions: Swipe to play, collect pencils, avoid obstacles

title: Zoo Pong
description: While the Zoo is closed, the Animols organized a competition to keep them entertained! Zoopong is a twist of the classic Pong game. Play through challenging levels with exciting power-ups with your favorite Animols!
instructions: Drag the Animol left and right. Hit the ball with the Animol to bounce the ball back. Score 3 goals before the opponents to advance the levels. Collect coins and unlock more Animols to play with!

title: Sushi Challenge
description: Be the ultimate sushi master! Match the sushi pieces via a variety of techniques. Beware, time runs out quickly. Match intelligently, and match fast!
instructions: Match the sushi pieces, to challenge the boss. Be the sushi master!

title: Fish Rescue Pull the Pin
description: In the new exciting game Fish Rescue: Pull the Pin, we would like to invite you to do the rescue of fish that have found themselves without their usual habitat. A certain design will be visible on the screen in front of you. You will see several niches in it. They will be separated by partitions. In one niche you will see a fish, and in another water. You will need to carefully study everything and remove a certain partition. Thus, you will open it and water will get to the fish.
instructions: Use mouse or touch the screen!

title: Perfect Salon
description: Some people really need a stylist.This is you who will help them out and win their hearts!In this game you can make a diverse makeup for completely different people, receive rewards for this and see the sincere emotions of people who are grateful to you for your work.
instructions: Change different colors of lipstick, eyeliner and powder to achieve an excellent look.

title: Jurassic Theft
description: Jurassic Theft is a cool platform game in which you try to steal some precious eggs from dinosaurs! The mad professor has travelled back in time to the Jurassic period to steal dinosaur eggs so he can start his own Jurassic theme park. You need to collect all the eggs that you can find while keeping the professor alive in this dangerous dinosaur filled environment. Watch out for the patrolling Velociraptors on the ground, Mosasaurus in the water and the Pterodactyls in the sky and the giant T-rex running around!
instructions: Use the arrow keys or touch screen to control the player.

title: Poopieman Voodo
description: Have fun with this new game Poopieman Voodoo here on kiz10 play it for free and have fun aiming at the little doll and destroy it with all your ammunition and in all the ways you can, complete all the missions of this entertaining fun game based on the classic poopieman game. Enjoy this fun and entertaining new game, the funny character will use his poop to practice and aim, destroy the little tied doll and improve your aim with this new game.
instructions: The objective of the game is to point and shoot in all possible ways to destroy the tied doll.

title: Jail Breaker
description: Prison break is a very dangerous thing, can you help our game protagonist to escape from prison smoothly? In this process, you need to select the correct items according to the prompts.
instructions: Tap to play.

title: Among Impostor Collapse
description: Collapse the among impostor blocks by connecting 2 or more similar impostors. Collapse 6 or more impostor to get a bomb. More points are awarded as larger connections are made.
instructions: Use mouse to play this html5 block games.

title: Yellow Balls
description: The simple yet dynamic Yellow Balls game will test your ability to respond quickly to changing circumstances. At the bottom of the screen is a yellow dot, if you click on it, shooting will begin. The balls will pop up and move up in a straight line to reach the target located at the top. In the upper left corner you will see a number. After you make a mistake three times the game starts again.
instructions: Use mouse or tap on the screen!

title: Slingshot Jetpack
description: Have you ever dreamed of flying a jet plane over the city? In the game Slingshot Jetpack, your dream will come true. Your task is to collect gold coins in the air and accurately reach the end of each level.
instructions: drag to move

title: Magic Pom
description: Magic Pom is a cute casual puzzle game! Connect 3 or more similar Poms to make points within the time limit and reach the objectives in each level. Gain points to collect Pom packs and buy new abilities. Songs: In-Game: Jump and Run - Tropical Mix (OpenGameArt) Shop: Buy something! - Autor: Cleyton Kauffman Magic: Run Around (Edited) - Autor: Yubatake Music Theme: Rainbow Forest - Autor: Quincas Moreira
instructions: Make points connecting Poms and reach the objectives to go to the next stage! Buy more cute Pom packs and new abilities to play.

title: Merge Cafe
description: Buy tasty cakes, merge them to unlock new recipes and serve them to cute falling customers! Start as a tea house and expand your range of fresh bakes. Filled with over 18 delectable bakery treats, from luxurious cookies to indulgent triple chocolate cakes!
instructions: Merge the same recipes and drag them to the customers

title: Sweet Candy Land
description: Everyone loves a good candy game. Match similar candies, fulfill the objectives within the given time and progress to the next level. How many levels can you reach?
instructions: Match similar candies

title: Find Seven Differences Animals
description: In the game Find Seven Differences - Animals you will find a full search for differences on ten fascinating levels with animals. Do not get any hints, if you do not have time, start again. The difference found will be marked with a red circle so that you do not return to it. Do not click mindlessly throughout the picture, get a warning. The game Find Seven Differences - Animals will make you focus and become more attentive, the differences are small, barely discernible, you have to sweat to find them.
instructions: Use mouse or tap on the screen!

title: Shaun The Sheep Flock Together
description: In Shaun the SHeep Flock Together you must herd the sheep to safety by matching their leotards. But be careful not to stack the sheeps higher than the bunting! Complete each level by herding as many sheep as you can.
instructions: Use the arrow keys to guide the falling flock.

title: Slimoban 2
description: Slimoban 2 is the sequel of the Sokoban-inspired game, Slimoban, about a little girl and her adventures in the dungeon full of big and dangerous slimes. In each level, you need to collect the golden coin, escape from the slimes, and destroy them if possible. The girl can collect magic potions that help to lift big wooden blocks and slimes. After lifting the blocks or the slimes, you need to drop them in the right places. There is also water in the game, and you can drop things in there. You can move blocks, collect them, and drop them. You also need to lure the slimes in the trap, throw boxes in them, and push them into the water. But all of these things you can do are not obligatory, the main thing you need to do to pass the level is to collect the coin.
instructions: WASD or arrow keys to move the character Space bar to skip your turn Left click to drop the boxes

title: Pawn Boss
description: Run your very own shop and try to spot hidden gems from customers. People are lining up to make a deal. Use your bargaining skills to get the price as low as possible before you buy it off of them. Be careful though because some items are fakes! Can you spot the differences before you make a purchasing mistake?
instructions: Line your business with gold, antique guns, jewelry, art - whatever you can get your hands on to make a profit

title: Persia Prince Dash
description: Prince of Persia Dash is a puzzle adventure game. Control an armored prince to collect gold coins and break through the dungeon. Arrow keys or mouse control movement
instructions: W -move Up; A - move Left; S - move Down; D - move Right; Or mouse control movement;

title: Cup Pong Challenge
description: Flick the ping pong ball into the cup and land the ball correctly. Last one standing wins this cup pong game! Lively atmosphere with simple gameplay and 3 different computer opponents.
instructions: Flick the ball into the cup

title: Falling Down Stairs Online
description: Falling Down Stairs is a high score arcade game. We always thinking about what will happen if we fell down the stairs. Now you will know the answer. Avoid the spikes, turn round with others. Do not drop down the stairs. It is an endless stair.
instructions: drag to move

title: Scratch & Guess Animals
description: How well do you know the animals? Scratch the cards, and try to guess them. We've developed an innovative and new scratching mechanic. Scratch as much as you like, but beware of the scratch-o-meter.
instructions: Scratch and guess the animals

title: Frenzy Farming
description: An immersive farming game, Frenzy Farming is here! In the Frenzy Farming game, you must first plant your farm and feed your chickens. The chickens will provide you with eggs. You can check the determined missions from the reserved area on the game screen. To plant more grass, you have to extract water from the well in exchange for Coins. You can get eggs with the chickens you produce, and you can produce eggs and bread. They will accompany you in the later levels in the cows. Cows produce milk, and you can combine the produced milk with bread to produce a cake. When you need money, you can sell your products in the market by clicking on the car icon and earn money. Fun and immersive farming simulator Frenzy Farming is completely free!
instructions: Mouse click and swipe

title: Mr. Lupato 2 Egyptian Pyramids Treasures
description: Mr. Lupato goes on a trip and needs your help to find Egyptian Pyramids treasures. Help him to jump and get all gems and keys. Open the door at the end of each level and get stars. Don't miss additional jumps, find secret items and collect beutiful gems. Complete all levels and enjoy this exciting adventure and funny platformer. Be careful, the number of jumps is limited. Mr. Lupato 2 Egyptian Pyramids Treasures Features: * Intuitive controls * Double jumps * Dangerous snakes and big spiders * 15 levels * 4 secret items
instructions: Use mouse or space and help Mr. Lupato to jump and collect all gems, keys and amulets.

title: Easter 2021 Collection
description: Collect the easter items in this html5 game. Press any easter item to start. Now move the 'mouse or finger tip' on identical adjacent items (horizontally, vertically or diagonally). Select at least 3 items. Release mouse button to make them match. Each 6th items will give a bonus. More than 7 items will give you a time bonus. Collect the target easter items within the giving time, or you will lose the game. What's the max level can you play?
instructions: Use mouse to play this html5 easter collection games.

title: Axe Hit Champ
description: Throw Axe to Blast the Targets, destroy moving objects Show your axe throwing skills to complete challenges in action games. Challenge yourself to make the better score playing Gold Hit Could you be the best of throwing Axe? ***** AMAZING FEATURE ***** - Axe throwing game for all ages anywhere and anytime - Designed for players of all generations and skill levels - Realistic 3D environment and HD graphics even for low-performing devices - Crush those targets and go all out for the best score! - More than 50 challenging battle axe throw - Easy and fun tap to play game - Aim for the moving object and tap to throw axe
instructions: Tap to throw the axe and smash the targets

title: Run Royale Knockout
description: The latest chaotic obstacle course battle royale is about to begin, are you ready? Use your skills to navigate through the crazy obstacles and beat all your opponents. Will you be the ultimate winner? Let's wait and see!
instructions: Click and drag the mouse to play.

title: Swipe Ball
description: In the Swipe Ball game, you must avoid the bombs and collect the diamonds around you. You have to use your reflexes and quickness while playing this game. Challenge your friends by achieving the highest score in Swipe Ball, a fun hypercasual game!
instructions: W,A,S,D or Arrow Keys

title: Dangerous Danny
description: Danny is a brave man and this time he decided he wants to reach the biggest depth anyone has ever dived before, help him achieve his goal and set a new record in deep-sea diving. Wild sea creatures, mines, and dangerous cliffs will stand in his way, can he manage to push through and achieve his goal?
instructions: Dive with Danny into the depths of the ocean, collect coins, evade wild animals, and try to reach the biggest depth anyone has ever achieved. Beware the dangers of mines, cliffs, and sharks, and remember to replenish your oxygen and health.

title: Waggle Balls 3D
description: Wobble a table and put all the gems in the holes. Press the left mouse button and move the mouse to control the table. and avoid obstacles. Pass as many levels as you can!
instructions: Press the left mouse button and move the mouse to control the table.

title: Instruments for Kids
description: Instruments For Kids is a very fun game! This game is designed for children, in which there is music from 4 instruments. In this game you can play piano, xylophone, harp and drums.
instructions: Use mouse or touch the screen!

title: Bouncing Eggs
description: Bouncing Eggs is a HTML5 Physics game. Throw the falling eggs in the basket by bouncing them on the cloth and reach the target of each of the ten levels.
instructions: Use arrows to move bunnies left/right

title: Totem Volcano
description: Tap to remove the blocks. Remove the right blocks, in the right sequence to bring the totem to the safe spot. Protect the villagers from the anger of the volcano!
instructions: Remove the blocks to save the totem and the villagers

title: Mees Kees Stacker
description: Mees Kees! The funniest teacher of the Netherlands. His way of teaching is quite different, and that makes him a very popular teacher. In this stacker game you will stack all kinds of different objects. Use blocks, bowling balls, bags and all kinds of other objects and try stacking them all on top of each other.
instructions: Stack all the objects and don't let them fall!

title: Jelly World
description: Click the mouse to operate the character, make the character jump, leap in the air to get diamonds, and fly to victory, and you can also get touch tools in the air to increase the game experience. You will be immersed in it, this feeling is so good.
instructions: Click to play.

title: Candy Crusher
description: Crush down the candy to become king of candies. Match 3 or more of the same candies together to remove them from play. Match 4 or 5 candies together to unlock bonus candies. Try to score as many points as possible within the limited amount of moves given. Level up to unlock additional board space in this fun online Candy Crush game.
instructions: Use mouse or finger to match 3 or more of the same candy.

title: Stair Run Online
description: Stair Run Online is an adventure running game. You need to collect bricks. Build stairs across the obstacles with bricks. Avoid the red zone. It is easy and funny. You will meet kinds of obstacles, try to take over them. Collect as many bricks as you can. When you climb the top of the mountain in the end, you could earn a lot of coins.
instructions: tap to build stairs.

title: Find The Difference Animal
description: You need to spot out the different animal within a lot of the similar ones before the time runs out. How fast can you make it? Many challenges to try out. PLAY NOW!
instructions: Tap on the different animal.

title: Wave Run
description: The game has only one move ball and a variety of obstacle at random. Use mouse or your finger to interact with the game to avoid crazy objects and have fun! Good Luck!
instructions: Use mouse or your finger to interact with the game and have fun!

title: Spider Trump
description: Spider Trump is a challenging game with a lot of levels to play. Swing Trump by shooting spider web to avoid the obstacles. Keep as many as possible his body-parts and reach the destination to be fully restored. Features: - Realistic physics - 72 levels PLAY NOW!
instructions: Arrow keys + Space bar/Shoot button
